{
  "texts": [
    "The meta-controller is trained using two single-sentence prediction datasets in GLUE, namely, SST-2 and CoLA.",
    "We split the original training dataset into a 9:1 ratio to generate train and validation datasets.",
    "The metacontroller, through meta-learning, learns to produce attention masks that are task-specific.",
    "These masks are then used to modify the attention weights obtained from the feature importance analysis.",
    "The process begins with pruning applied to subsets (k-instances) of the training instances and then continues iteratively until all instances have been considered."
  ]
}